T01.name: Help? Click here!
T01.info:
Everyone needs a solid foundation!

Upgrade, hire or buy stuff to make money!

If you buy stuff, you unlock more stuff!

Click on the icons for more information.

T03.info:
If you want to buy multiple things at once, use the buymore button!

How many clicks do you really need?

Hotkey: T

T04.name: Departments
T04.info:
Upgrade your management to unlock more departments!

Build the departments of your company with your management points.

Build your departments to unlock more stuff.

T05.name: Prestige
T05.info:
You can restart your game to progress even further!

Get as much money as you can and if you feel your progress slowing down, get the prestige points and restart the game with a bonus. The money you earn is stored in your savings. Prestige points are usefull in many ways and speed up your game.

Go to the menu to cash in the prestige.

Hotkey: P

T06.name: Notation
T06.info:
All numbers under 1000 are shown normal, over 1000 the notation is the following:
1000 = 1 K
1000000 = 1 M
1000000000 = 1 B
1000000000000 = 1 T

For numbers over 1000000000000000 (1 Qa, 1e15) the scientific notation is used.

T07.name: Ascension
T07.info:
You can restart your game and reset your prestige points to progress even further!

Earn acension level to unlock more features.

Go to the menu to ascend...

Hotkey: A

T08.name: Events
T08.info:
Events are gamplay features that are only available during a specific period of time.

The event timer is showing the hours left until the event is closed.

By completing certain tasks during a event you get a bonus that will stay after the event is closed.

T09.name: Operation
